{
  "texts": [
    "The number of participants and training and testing trials follow exactly as described for the human experiment 38.",
    "In particular, for each of the 24 simulated participants, the weights were initialized with a different seed of the random number generator.",
    "They each experi enced two stages: training and testing.",
    "Note that the pretraining stage performed in the human experiment was not simulated here as its goal was to make human participants familiar with the setup and devices.",
    "In the training stage, the model experienced 24 blocks of trials."
  ]
}